  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t感謝<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZmFjZWJvb2suY29tL2dyb3Vwcy8zNDAzMjMyNjMyMjU5NDQvdXNlci8xMDAwNTAyNTI3Mzc2NzQv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/340323263225944/user/100050252737674/\">臉書網友</a>分享。對中國朋友來說，這是很不錯的臺灣歷史綱要，儘管在視角和史觀方面仍然有改進的巨大空間。對於其中涉及到的歷史事件，不妨將其作為一部索引，自主蒐集和分析多方面的材料，在頭腦中立體化地重建歷史的複雜真相。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzcyYjRkN2FiOWFlNmMwNjUzNTk3LmpwZz93aWR0aD04NDMmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMTE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/372b4d7ab9ae6c0653597.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1311\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/372b4d7ab9ae6c0653597.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1311\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/372b4d7ab9ae6c0653597.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1311\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGI4NGVlYjAzOTZiOTUzYTEyYTc4LmpwZz93aWR0aD04NDMmaGVpZ2h0PTEyOTc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4b84eeb0396b953a12a78.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1297\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4b84eeb0396b953a12a78.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1297\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4b84eeb0396b953a12a78.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1297\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTY0ZWQ0OGM4MzlkY2Q1Y2M0OGZiLmpwZz93aWR0aD04NDMmaGVpZ2h0PTEyNjI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/564ed48c839dcd5cc48fb.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1262\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/564ed48c839dcd5cc48fb.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1262\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/564ed48c839dcd5cc48fb.jpg?width=843&amp;height=1262\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/i